{"tid":1966113,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"食羊肉你鐘意食有騷味定無騷味","createTime":"2020-04-10T03:20:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T13:57:05.000Z","uid":331739,"like":187,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"e7c8c195741e5e29c4366f2de2856e569c1e8546","tid":1966113,"uid":331739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T03:20:12.000Z","msg":"想做個統計<br />\n因為香港好多餐廳賣嘅羊肉都好唔騷<br />\n覺得係因為好多香港人唔食得騷<br />\n成日都聽到人話唔鐘意太騷嘅羊肉<br />\n但我係勁鐘意浸騷味<br />\n以前食過新疆菜嘅手抓羊肉 騷到阿媽都唔認得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />勁正<br />\n但係好似好多香港人鐘意唔騷嘅羊肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鐘意騷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔鐘意騷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔食羊肉=唔好禁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b9dca5ebbc563cbb075175cc354c5cd1c6790b4","tid":1966113,"uid":246422,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T03:21:04.000Z","msg":"唔食騷不如唔好食羊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"656a0228d33501fd1cd8427155b0bce9f0369a1a","tid":1966113,"uid":43663,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T03:22:33.000Z","msg":"食羊肉唔食騷既話不如食牛肉算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec14f2dbf085d109616dc728bc4007fbdc11d78d","tid":1966113,"uid":263223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3b9dca5ebbc563cbb075175cc354c5cd1c6790b4","tid":1966113,"uid":246422,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T03:21:04.000Z","msg":"唔食騷不如唔好食羊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T03:22:43.000Z","msg":"我都係咁話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9816b061bd9758e6f2861ff50050c9907ccd1e15","tid":1